txt.en: The leader of the Scholar's Guild has asked you to compile your research on the Enemy into a pamphlet for the Rangers.
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nDraught a Morgul pamphlet.
Execute the recipe for a Morgul pamphlet

'Minas Morgul, Morgul Vale, Morgul crests! You'd think an enemy so powerful would be capable of being the slightest bit creative with their naming. Go bring me some records from Minas Morgul. Compile your findings in a... Morgul pamphlet or something.'
